      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOAH BONKERS (7) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 340m behind Rosacky Rayo (20.07) in a Grade 3/4. Was in the money the start prior. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. SHE'S TIP TOP (1) was a brilliant winner two back scoring by 0.8 lengths but drifted back latest and safely held when 8th and beaten 5.5 lengths at Q Lakeside (20.17). One of the main contenders. SALAMAT (5) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only a nose from Nicmac Star in second (19.90) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Winning chance. JAKEY BLUE (8) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
